The paper deals with the analysis of facial expressions, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper discusses the applications of recognizing micro-expressions in psychotherapy, which falls under human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also uses machine learning techniques for recognition, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the use of feature difference contrast, which is a technique commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR).
